@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}
<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<p class="mb-4">This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and protect your personal information on our forum-based site dedicated to logging campus incidents and facilitating investigations.</p>

<h3 class="mt-4">Information We Collect</h3>
<ul class="mt-3">
    <li>User-Provided Information: When you register on our site or when reports or investigations are logged</li>
    <li>Automatically Collected Information: We may automatically collect certain data.</li>
</ul>

<h3 class="mt-4">How We Use Your Information</h3>
<p class="mt-3">We use the information we collect for purposes including:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Logging and investigating incidents.</li>
    <li>Communicating with you about your reports and investigations.</li>
    <li>Improving our site and services.</li>
</ul>

<h3 class="mt-4">Information Sharing</h3>
<p class="mt-3">We do not share your personal information with third parties.</p>

<h3 class="mt-4">Data Security</h3>
<p class="mt-3">We take reasonable measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access and disclosure.</p>

<h3 class="mt-4">Changes to This Privacy Policy</h3>
<p class="mt-3">We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. Please review this page for any changes.</p>

<h3 class="mt-4">GDPR Compliancy</h3>
<p class="mt-3">You may delete your personal data at any point on your profile page.</p>
<p>Should you need to have any images deleted from the site for misuse, you may kindly contact us to do so.</p>

<p class="mt-3">If you have any questions about our Privacy Policy, please contact us on info@nemesys.com.</p>
